{
  "id": "RAW_632e3aaa",
  "title": "英伟达 H200 获准出口中国的三个关键问题",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mjc1NjM3MjY2MA==&mid=2691562243&idx=1&sn=f3b28cd95d7f3a4f58f00d3baa39fa49",
  "date": "2025-12-09 03:58:00",
  "author": "腾讯科技",
  "siteName": "腾讯科技",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-widget=\"image\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;display: inline-block;max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-size: 12px;display: flex;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);align-items: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"544078591\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.582\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1000\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;border: 0px none;height: 403.836px;width: 694px;max-width: 100%;border-radius: 4px;display: inline-block;aspect-ratio: 1.7185 / 1;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=398793ea&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fow6przZuPIEW8gMMI1qtBBMvXQcRdfShtQWdkaRCHtYI8o4toqfzXpu4kYyic0k5Miak13oscQKECcHpPha1tqrA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></span><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);display: block;font-size: 12px;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">黄仁勋、苏姿丰“带货”，图片由AI生成</span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:right;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bolder;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">文丨苏扬</span></span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:right;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bolder;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">编辑丨徐青阳</span></span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">“在国家安全得到保障的前提下，美国即将允许英伟达向中国大陆等地区的客户出口H200产品。”特朗普美国时间12月8日在社交媒体上宣布了这一“交易”，作为回报，英伟达需要给美国政府25%的销售分成。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">对此，英伟达回应称：“向商业客户供应H200是一种值得肯定的举措。”</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">H200的出口解禁这个事情上，有三个问题值得关注：</span></span></span><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bolder;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">流程什么时候落地、对谁是利好，对国产生态会带来什么影响？</span></span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">H200的解禁实际上早有传闻，之前的争议点在于：美国行政和立法部门之间的博弈。或者说，如何消除美国国会层面对“保持美国AI继续领先能力”丧失的疑虑。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">“</span></span></span><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bolder;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">美国商务部和国会不一定乐见，现在这种提议到最后落地，概率要打个问号</span></span></span></strong><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。”此前一位科技政策研究员谈及H200的解禁传闻时说。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bolder;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">相关流程需要多长时间？</span></span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">从目前特朗普在社交媒体官宣允许H200出口的这个动作来看，上述疑虑已经得到了安抚。很重要的一点，</span></span></span><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bolder;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">是过去一段时间黄仁勋在各种场合吹风，“不确定大陆客户会不会要”、“H200已经不够先进”</span></span></span></strong><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但黄仁勋只是添油加醋，更重要的信号是特朗普官宣的动作。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">此前H20拿到出口许可，也是通过特朗普在社交媒体上官宣——这意味着美国行政、立法等之间基本达成了共识</span></span></span><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bolder;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。“就算有人唱反调，特朗普依旧有制约的工具。”前述科技政策研究员强调。</span></span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">从特朗普的官宣的节奏来看，各方对于H200解禁的共识已有，剩下的就是如何解决政策相关的流程和执行问题，这些都还需要时间来处理。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">“</span></span></span><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bolder;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">他不是一句话说可以卖了就开始卖，走正常的法规也需要时间</span></span></span></strong><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，而且直接批许可，也与出口管制条例不相符。”另一位长期关注科技政策的研究员强调。</span></span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 8px 24px;white-space:normal;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:19px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><mark style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"></mark><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bolder;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">H200的性能落后了吗？</span></span></span></strong></h2>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">事实上，达成H200出口的共识，建立在其性能已“相对落后”的基础之上。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">2023年11月，英伟达正式发布H200，2024年第二季度开始向全球客户和云服务厂商供货，且第二季度下旬进入量产期，第三季度后开启大量交货，单卡3万-4万美元，8卡服务器大致在30万美元左右。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这款芯片采用台积电4N先进工艺，核心为GH100GPU，内置800亿晶体管，热设计功耗为700W，还配备了NVLink 4互联技术，拥有 18 条链路、900GB/s 的互联带宽。搭载HBM3e的 GPU，拥有141GB显存，显存带宽高达4.8TB/s。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">2024年，H200是绝对先进的产品，FP16算力高达1979T，而特供中国市场的H20只有148T，而FP8算力更是高达3958T，H20则只有296T，且H200互联带宽也是H20的一倍，达到900GB/s。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但是到了2025年年底，基于Blackwell架构的B200等产品上线，并成为行业顶流，H200退居其次，成为一款性能“相对落后”的产品。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">“符合预期，”一位产业研究员谈及H200出口解禁话题时说，</span></span></span><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bolder;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">“放Hopper架构，不放Blackwell架构，也能和国内交代，‘我们还领先一代半’，中国客户也能买到想要的</span></span></span></strong><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。”</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">总体而言，特朗普在社交媒体上宣布允许H200出口，等同于基本消除了各界担忧</span></span></span><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bolder;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，本质上还是H200已经不代表先进算力了</span></span></span></strong><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 8px 24px;white-space:normal;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:19px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><mark style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"></mark><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bolder;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">能否获得中国大陆市场的“解冻”</span></span></span></strong></h2>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">当然，前面提到了交易对价——25%的销售收入，这个比例相比H20出口许可的15%，涨了10个百分点。按中国大陆单季度100亿美元的营收贡献估算，</span></span></span><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bolder;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">H200获准出口每年至少给美国政府带来100亿美元的“好处费”。</span></span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在好处这件事情上，一直作为“苦主”的英伟达，将面临中国大陆市场销售“解冻”。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">此前，黄仁勋在诸多场合都表示“中国大陆市场份额为0”，H200获准出口将为其带来新的机会，尤其是相比阉割的H20，其性能大幅度领先，更容易获得客户的青睐。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">“中国客户的模型都是适配Hopper架构GPU做的，”前述产业研究员强调。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在他看来，</span></span></span><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bolder;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Hopper架构现阶段的吸引力要比Blackwell架构更大，“B卡都没适配过，不然算子，工具链，底层软件都要重新做一遍，那工程量更大。”</span></span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">简单概括，对模型开发商来说，从Hopper架构迁移到其他新架构，需要重新开发运算模块、搭建专属工具流程以及重构底层对接程序，这些都需要大量的人力、工程和时间成本。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bolder;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">站在英伟达的立场上，H200销售的利润空间也要比H20理想</span></span></span></strong><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，后者基于H100阉割而来，会增加制造端的成本，而H200不需要做任何的阉割，作为一款老产品，平均毛利率有望接近甚至是超过80%。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">可以说，黄仁勋在中美之间来回穿梭，等到了一个每年价值上百亿美元的好消息。毕竟在过去的一段时间里，英伟达被谷歌TPU的叙事搅得焦头烂额，甚至不得不亲自下场，高喊“我们更强”、“我们不是竞争关系”。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">根据此前公布的数据，2024自然年度，英伟达在中国大陆市场的全部收入为171亿美元。如果最终H200的出口顺利，中国市场数据中心产品的收入有望创下新高。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">也正是因为这一点，</span></span></span><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bolder;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">英伟达美股周一盘后交易中快速拉升，涨超1%，市值涨超450亿美元。</span></span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">不过需要注意，英伟达并非唯一一家获得放行的企业，此前AMD董事长兼CEO苏姿丰也已经对外确认获得解禁，向大陆客户出口MI308芯片。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">关于此次H200的出口，黄仁勋表达过一个担忧——不确定大陆客户会不会要H200，暗示这款产品的性能已经不先进。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但如果从算力的角度来看，H200显然比此前的H20具有优势。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bolder;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">业内普遍预估其算力在H20的8倍左右，而按FP16的纸面数据来计算，H200也是H20的13倍</span></span></span></strong><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">+，要知道，H20相对国产产品来说，算力上都已经不具备优势了，这也可以解释为什么前期H20虽然解禁，但没有客户采购，以及为什么现阶段美国要抛出一个新的H200出口方案的原因。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">根据2025年早期披露的消息，多家大厂总计向英伟达下了160亿美元的H20订单，但最终未能交付，随着H200的解禁，这些需求将转换为新订单，在2026年释放。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">“国内大厂压制了2个季度的需求，资本开支会累加到明年，明年的需求很大。”前述产业研究员强调。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">不过，H200获准向中国大陆客户出售，对国产的影响引发各方关注，</span></span></span><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bolder;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">多位国产算力芯片相关的从业者表示，放开H200与国产并不直接冲突。</span></span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">“H200对中国客户具有实际应用价值，目前国内的云厂基本都是用于训练，做推理性价比不高。而国产AI芯片，目前大部分都是用于推理的场景。”一位算力分销商强调。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">凯腾律所合伙人韩利杰说：“</span></span></span><strong style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bolder;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">主要还是帮英伟达赚钱</span></span></span></strong><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，与中国本土产品竞争只是其次。”</span></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章深度分析了英伟达 H200 获准出口中国的三个核心问题，包括落地流程、市场影响及对国产算力生态的潜在冲击。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章深度分析了英伟达 H200 获准出口中国的三个核心问题，包括落地流程、市场影响及对国产算力生态的潜在冲击。",
  "summary": "文章详细探讨了英伟达 H200 获准出口中国这一消息背后的关键问题。首先，分析了这一政策从官宣到正式落地的流程和所需时间，指出行政和立法部门已基本达成共识。其次，文章通过对比 H200 与 H20、B200 的性能，说明 H200 在当前的“相对落后”是解禁的关键因素，但其 Hopper 架构对中国客户仍具极高吸引力，解决了模型适配的痛点。最后，文章预估 H200 出口将为英伟达带来巨额收益，并讨论了其对国内算力市场和国产 AI 芯片的潜在影响，认为 H200 主要面向训练场景，不与国产芯片在推理市场直接冲突，但长期效应仍需观察。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "H200 出口解禁的流程已在行政和立法层面达成共识。",
      "explanation": "文章指出特朗普的官宣意味着政策层面的阻碍已基本消除，但具体的法规和执行流程仍需时间，并非立即生效。"
    },
